🔌 Circuit Design Summaries
🚨 Project 1: Motion Detection System
Components:

PIR Sensor (Sensor 1)

Ultrasonic Sensor (Sensor 2)

LED (Output)

Connections:

PIR Sensor:

VCC → 5V

GND → GND

OUT → D2

Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04):

VCC → 5V

GND → GND

Trig → D3

Echo → D4

LED:

Anode → D7 via 220Ω resistor

Cathode → GND

☀️ Project 2: Solar Light Detection & Rotation
Components:

2 × Photoresistors (LDRs)

Servo Motor

Connections:

Photoresistor 1:

One side → A0

Other side → 5V

10kΩ resistor between A0 and GND

Photoresistor 2:

One side → A1

Other side → 5V

10kΩ resistor between A1 and GND

Servo Motor:

Signal → D9

VCC → 5V

GND → GND

🛡️ Project 3: Mars Emergency Flap
Components:

Potentiometer

Push Button

LED

Servo Motor

Connections:

Potentiometer:

Left pin → 5V

Right pin → GND

Middle pin → A0

Push Button:

One terminal → D2

Other terminal → GND

(Internal pull-up enabled in code)

LED:

Anode → D7 via 220Ω resistor

Cathode → GND

Servo Motor:

Signal → D9

VCC → 5V

GND → GND
